    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound 2011 BMW M3 (E92) featuring the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This high-revving powerplant, equipped with eight individual throttle bodies and an 8,400 RPM redline, delivers linear power through a crisp 7-speed M-DCT dual-clutch transmission. The chassis architecture remains rigid, supported by Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and a precision-tuned M-variable differential lock for superior corner-exit traction. This example has been properly maintained with recent fluid analysis and throttle actuator service, ensuring the VANOS system and rod bearings remain within healthy operating parameters. It is an honest, driver-focused machine with excellent turn-in response and the unmistakable induction note of an atmospheric V8.",
      "price": 34500.0,
