      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously cared-for 2017 Sport Executive Sedan that perfectly balances spirited performance with everyday usability. The exterior is finished in a deep Metallic Charcoal that still holds a brilliant shine, though close inspection will reveal minor stone chips on the front bumper consistent with highway driving. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of black Dakota leather; the seats remain firm and supportive, showing only light natural creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster. All electronic features, including the premium surround-sound system and navigation, function flawlessly. Mechanically, this vehicle is in excellent health, having followed a strict synthetic oil change regimen every 5,000 miles. The turbocharged engine delivers smooth, consistent power, and the transmission shifts with precision. It recently received a fresh set of all-season tires and a brake fluid flush, making it completely turn-key for its next owner. This is a reliable, honest vehicle that looks as good in a professional parking lot as it does on a winding back road.",
      "price": 34500.0,
